data.description: New Price Improvement. Welcome to this stunning 6-bedroom, 6-full bathroom home nestled on a quiet cul-de-sac. This all-brick colonial-style residence exudes elegance and offers a wealth of desirable features. Upon entering, you are greeted by a grand two-level foyer, adorned with an abundance of natural light that cascades throughout the entire house. The main level boasts a versatile bedroom, currently utilized as an office, perfect for those who work from home or desire a private study space. This remarkable property offers two primary suites, ensuring unparalleled convenience and flexibility. Each primary suite features a lavish en-suite bathroom with a soaking tub, providing the perfect retreat for relaxation and pampering. The gourmet kitchen is a culinary enthusiast's dream, featuring elegant granite countertops and top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances. Whether you're hosting an intimate dinner or entertaining a large gathering, this well-appointed kitchen is sure to impress. The basement of this home is an entertainer's paradise, boasting an in-home theatre where you can enjoy your favorite movies and shows in the comfort of your own space. The basement also offers limitless possibilities for customization, allowing you to create the ultimate recreational area tailored to your preferences. Step outside to the expansive deck and patio, providing the perfect canvas for your personal touches and outdoor gatherings. Imagine savoring the warm summer evenings with family and friends, creating lasting memories in this idyllic setting. This property also features a 3-car garage, ensuring ample space for your vehicles and additional storage needs. The location of this home is ideal for those working at the nearby Naval Support Facility Indian Head, providing a convenient commute. With its move-in ready condition, this home is perfectly timed for summer family events. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your own and enjoy the luxurious lifestyle it offers. Schedule your private tour today.
